e,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.20260420131310"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420131432","id":"zettel.20260420131432","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.20260420131311","position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":14,"offset":1960},"end":{"line":50,"column":39,"offset":1985},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.20260420131311"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420131432","id":"zettel.20260420131432","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.literature.context-anchoring","position":{"start":{"line":54,"column":3,"offset":2064},"end":{"line":54,"column":42,"offset":2103},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.literature.context-anchoring"}},{"from":{"fname":"zettel","id":"zettel","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":93,"column":3,"offset":7926},"end":{"line":93,"column":28,"offset":7951},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420131432"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.literature.context-anchoring","id":"zettel.literature.context-anchoring","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":180,"column":3,"offset":12380},"end":{"line":180,"column":28,"offset":12405},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420131432"}],"anchors":{"gagasan":{"type":"header","text":"Gagasan","value":"gagasan","line":15,"column":0,"depth":2},"mengapa-ini-penting":{"type":"header","text":"Mengapa Ini Penting","value":"mengapa-ini-penting","line":19,"column":0,"depth":2},"maksud-overhead-dokumentasi":{"type":"header","text":"Maksud Overhead Dokumentasi","value":"maksud-overhead-dokumentasi","line":23,"column":0,"depth":2},"biaya-kehilangan-konteks":{"type":"header","text":"Biaya Kehilangan Konteks","value":"biaya-kehilangan-konteks","line":33,"column":0,"depth":2},"kapan-enggak-worth-it":{"type":"header","text":"Kapan Enggak Worth It","value":"kapan-enggak-worth-it","line":44,"column":0,"depth":2},"kapan-worth-it":{"type":"header","text":"Kapan Worth It","value":"kapan-worth-it","line":52,"column":0,"depth":2},"hubungan-ke-zettel-lain":{"type":"header","text":"Hubungan ke Zettel Lain","value":"hubungan-ke-zettel-lain","line":59,"column":0,"depth":2},"sumber":{"type":"header","text":"Sumber","value":"sumber","line":65,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"zettel","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"nilai-anchoring-ditentukan-oleh-overhead-dokumentasi-versus-biaya-kehilangan-konteks\">Nilai anchoring ditentukan oleh overhead dokumentasi versus biaya kehilangan konteks<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#nilai-anchoring-ditentukan-oleh-overhead-dokumentasi-versus-biaya-kehilangan-konteks\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"gagasan\">Gagasan<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#gagasan\"></a></h2>\n<p>Kalau bikin dokumen lebih mahal daripada nge-rebuild sesi, itu tanda belum cocok.</p>\n<h2 id=\"mengapa-ini-penting\">Mengapa Ini Penting<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#mengapa-ini-penting\"></a></h2>\n<p>Ini jadi alat evaluasi praktis, bukan prinsip dogmatis.</p>\n<h2 id=\"maksud-overhead-dokumentasi\">Maksud Overhead Dokumentasi<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#maksud-overhead-dokumentasi\"></a></h2>\n<p>Overhead dokumentasi berarti biaya tambahan yang muncul karena membuat, memperbarui, dan memelihara dokumentasi feature. Ini bisa berupa:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>waktu menulis ringkasan keputusan,</li>\n<li>usaha menyinkronkan dokumen dengan kode dan status nyata,</li>\n<li>review dan percobaan agar dokumen tetap akurat.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Jika fitur sangat kecil atau hanya butuh satu sesi, biaya ini bisa lebih besar daripada cuma mengulang sedikit konteks di chat.</p>\n<h2 id=\"biaya-kehilangan-konteks\">Biaya Kehilangan Konteks<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#biaya-kehilangan-konteks\"></a></h2>\n<p>Biaya kehilangan konteks terjadi ketika sesi baru harus membangun ulang semua asumsi. Ini nyata dalam bentuk:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>waktu yang terbuang menjelaskan lagi keputusan sebelumnya,</li>\n<li>AI yang mengulang alternatif yang sudah ditolak,</li>\n<li>kesalahan karena alasan keputusan tidak lagi terlihat,</li>\n<li>sesi panjang yang dipaksa bertahan supaya konteks tidak hilang.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Contoh praktis: jika sebuah fitur butuh diskusi multi-hari, tanpa feature document maka setiap sesi akan butuh rekap ulang, dan risiko AI lupa alasan <code>RetryQueue</code> ditolak atau constraint <code>email-only</code> semakin besar.</p>\n<h2 id=\"kapan-enggak-worth-it\">Kapan Enggak Worth It<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#kapan-enggak-worth-it\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>task eksplorasi sekali jalan yang selesai dalam satu jam,</li>\n<li>bug fix kecil dengan konteks jelas dari kode yang ada,</li>\n<li>sesion proof-of-concept yang tidak akan dilanjutkan.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Dalam kasus ini, membuat dokumentasi feature adalah overhead yang tidak sebanding.</p>\n<h2 id=\"kapan-worth-it\">Kapan Worth It<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#kapan-worth-it\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>fitur yang tersebar beberapa sesi,</li>\n<li>keputusan arsitektur yang kompleks,</li>\n<li>tim atau AI session berganti-ganti,</li>\n<li>ketika kehilangan konteks berpotensi menyebabkan ratusan menit rework.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"hubungan-ke-zettel-lain\">Hubungan ke Zettel Lain<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#hubungan-ke-zettel-lain\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Mendukung <a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.context-anchoring\">Context Anchoring — memindahkan konteks keputusan dari chat ke dokumen hidup</a> — klaim diambil dari Paragraf 35.</li>\n<li>Lihat juga <a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131310\">Percakapan AI adalah medium berpikir, bukan tempat penyimpanan keputusan</a> — tesis utama bahwa chat AI adalah medium berpikir, bukan tempat penyimpanan keputusan.</li>\n<li>Lihat juga <a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131311\">Kolaborasi manusia multi-hari memindahkan memori kerja ke dokumen bersama</a> — baseline kolaborasi manusia yang transfer konteks ke dokumen.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"sumber\">Sumber<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#sumber\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.context-anchoring\">Context Anchoring — memindahkan konteks keputusan dari chat ke dokumen hidup</a> — Paragraf 35</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a class=\"color-tag\" style=\"--tag-color: #a03623;\" href=\"/sotoy/notes/tags.zettel\">zettel</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">ai-collaboration (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"color-tag\" style=\"--tag-color: #f0944d;\" href=\"/sotoy/notes/tags.knowledge-management\">knowledge-management</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">context-anchoring (Private)</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.context-anchoring\">Context Anchoring — memindahkan konteks keputusan dari chat ke dokumen hidup</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.github.io/sotoy/)\n- [My GitHub](https://github.com/zeihanaulia)\n- [My Twitter / X](https://x.com/zeihanaulia)\n\nThanks for stopping by. If you have feedback or want to chat, feel free to reach out.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"dendronVersion":"0.83.0","vaults":[{"fsPath":"vault"}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"childOfDomain"},"scratch":{"name":"scratch","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd.HHmmss","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain"},"task":{"name":"","dateFormat":"","addBehavior":"childOfCurrent","statusSymbols":{"":" ","wip":"w","done":"x","assigned":"a","moved":"m","blocked":"b","delegated":"l","dropped":"d","pending":"y"},"prioritySymbols":{"H":"h